{"tid":518342,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[印度野] 有無人知小食塊餅同青醬叫咩名？","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T11:38:43.000Z","uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"124c1feceb009c62faee1dca8708f892c5ee32b4","tid":518342,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/162921_fd874cd2b1406a5106bb08f6f981d265.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F162921_fd874cd2b1406a5106bb08f6f981d265.png&h=6691056b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇左張單佢淨係寫Open food<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚好食 仲要$10有五塊<br />\n個青醬又係又香又酸 好撚正<br />\n<br />\n利申係蓬萊食 次次都淨係指住塊餅同佢講more<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a166602ab0356435c8ac30ca9bfa3ee5ea8901","tid":518342,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"印度薄餅"},{"pid":"542518202e9580f1aca9747b5e47b39cecd2e9e7","tid":518342,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"屎黎"},{"pid":"e1bf1cedacdb7b1ff5b6d54688287e1b5396bf29","tid":518342,"uid":22762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"papadum<br />\n<br />\nmint yogurt"},{"pid":"0301e6737a70755f631cf2152fbc144d736df706","tid":518342,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1bf1cedacdb7b1ff5b6d54688287e1b5396bf29","tid":518342,"uid":22762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"papadum<br />\n<br />\nmint yogurt"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒巴打！"},{"p